data.title: Office of Cannabis Policy
data.text:
Job Title: Owner/Operator

Businesses: ORIGINs, Shwaggle Farms, Sundown Beverage Co.

Seat Held on Workgroup: Caregiver Representative

Biography: David Vickers grew up in Augusta, Maine, and graduated from Cony High School in 1992.

After graduating from Williams College in 1996, he returned home to Maine to build a career and family with his wife, Katie. David is the proud owner and operator of businesses in both the adult-use and medical cannabis industry known as ORIGINs (retail), Shwaggle Farms (cultivation), and Sundown Beverage Co. (manufacturing).
